sportError, InvalidToolPayload, CleanupFailed\",\n./tasks/prd.json:321:      \"notes\": \"Add reserved name list and policy check in mcp-runtime. Wire cleanup hook into agent loop in application crate. ComputerUseLifecycle per chicago-mcp-contract.md.\",\n./tasks/prd.json:339:        \"Tool visibility is a pure function of mode + capability policy (no side effects)\",\n./tasks/prd.json:359:      \"title\": \"Mode-aware tool visibility\",\n./tasks/prd.json:360:      \"description\": \"As a user, I want tool visibility to change based on the current assistant mode so that irrelevant tools are hidden.\",\n./tasks/prd.json:362:        \"Each mode defines a tool allowlist\",\n./tasks/prd.json:363:        \"ToolRegistry supports filtered view by mode via definitions_for_mode(mode) method\",\n./tasks/prd.json:364:        \"Brief mode hides high-risk tools\",\n./tasks/prd.json:365:        \"Tool allowlist output is deterministic and testable\",\n./tasks/prd.json:373:      \"notes\": \"Add definitions_for_mode(mode) method to ToolRegistry. Wire into agent loop's tool list construction.\",\n./tasks/prd.json:536:        \"8-state machine (UltraplanPhase): Idle, Launching, Polling, AwaitingInput, Approved, Stopping, Completed, Failed\",\n./tasks/prd.json:537:        \"Transitions: Idle→Launching; Launching→Polling|Failed; Polling→AwaitingInput|Approved|Failed|Stopping; AwaitingInput→Polling|Stopping; Approved→Completed; Stopping→Completed|Failed\",\n./tasks/prd.json:544:        \"UltraplanError variants: DisabledByPolicy, AlreadyActive, LaunchFailed, PollTimeout, ApprovalFailed, ArchiveFailed, Transport(String)\",\n./tasks/prd.json:604:        \"TeamMemError variants: AuthUnavailable, Unauthorized, ConflictExhausted, PathValidationFailed, SecretDetected, FileTooLarge, EntryLimitExceeded, StorageWriteError, UpstreamTimeout\",\n./tasks/prd.json:660:      \"title\": \"AgentTool and TaskStopTool integration\",\n./tasks/prd.json:661:      \"description\": \"As a user, I want the coo