exist with current REPL mode without behavior regression\",\n./tasks/prd.json:804:      \"notes\": \"Create `crates/cli/src/cmd/tui.rs` and wire command in clap definitions. Add a small `ui` module for draw loop and terminal setup/teardown guards.\",\n./tasks/prd.json:814:      \"title\": \"Ratatui streaming renderer for assistant and tool events\",\n./tasks/prd.json:815:      \"description\": \"As a user, I want streaming model output and tool execution events rendered incrementally in the TUI so that I can follow progress in real time.\",\n./tasks/prd.json:817:        \"LLM content deltas append to the active assistant message in the conversation pane\",\n./tasks/prd.json:818:        \"Tool start/finish events render as structured timeline entries with success/failure markers\",\n./tasks/prd.json:828:      \"notes\": \"Build a `UiState` model decoupled from draw calls. Reuse existing stream events from `agent.rs` via channel/event adapter into ratatui draw loop.\",\n./tasks/prd.json:839:      \"title\": \"Ratatui input editing and IME-safe text entry\",\n./tasks/prd.json:840:      \"description\": \"As a CJK user, I want reliable input editing in TUI mode so that composition, cursor movement, and submission work correctly.\",\n./tasks/prd.json:862:      \"title\": \"Tool approval modal in ratatui\",\n./tasks/prd.json:863:      \"description\": \"As a user, I want a clear in-TUI tool approval modal so that I can safely approve or deny tool executions without leaving full-screen mode.\",\n./tasks/prd.json:865:        \"When a tool requires confirmation, show a modal with tool name, parameter summary, and risk level\",\n./tasks/prd.json:866:        \"Modal supports allow/deny/always-allow actions matching existing CLI semantics\",\n./tasks/prd.json:867:        \"Decision persists for session when always-allow is selected\",\n./tasks/prd.json:868:        \"Deny action resumes agent loop cleanly and logs decision in conversation pane\",\n./tasks/prd.json:876:      \"no